law.text:
As used in this subtitle:
"Association" means the Joint Underwriting Association established pursuant to the provisions of this subtitle;
"Legal professional liability insurance" means insurance as defined in KRS 304.5-070(1)(j);
"Commissioner" means the commissioner of the Department of Insurance; and
"Net direct premiums" means gross direct premiums written on the lines of insurance set forth in KRS 304.41-030(1) as computed by the commissioner of insurance, less return premiums for the unused or unabsorbed portions of premium deposits.
